Text: a must own album if your a fan of the genre. btw I didnt get this album from here so dont know the quality.

Excellent rip, but I should add that this is the initial blue-label "Jazz Masterpieces" digital remaster, which has a very different sound than all the other editions I've heard. It sounds much more "reverby" and crystalline than, for example, the Legacy remaster, and Chambers' bass sounds... odd.
